{"tid":2356019,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"返內地發展陷困境，藍絲【胡杏兒】嘆冇機會演女一","createTime":"2021-01-06T13:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T03:04:39.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c0b4d0810ed8c264cba00f5820d66e21966f1ce5","tid":2356019,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3fDPCo2cXBvFC03t0cdw9A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-01/6f6bc580-4fde-11eb-abed-c7618bd491c6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3fDPCo2cXBvFC03t0cdw9A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NS4yNjMxNTc4OTQ3MzY5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-01%2F6f6bc580-4fde-11eb-abed-c7618bd491c6&h=8e96472d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近宣布懷有第三胎的胡杏兒，剛剛在內地綜藝節目《演員請就位2》擊敗一眾實力派演員，奪得冠軍寶座。儘管如此，但她對於自己在內地發展仍然沒有多大的信心，她近日在內地節目《送一百位女孩回家》中就大嘆自己面臨演員的困境，更大方坦承沒有出演女主角的機會。<br />\n<br />\n內地演藝人才眾多，連香港「三料視后」都自覺於內地發展面臨困境，胡杏兒說：「沒有女一演了現在，我覺得很難。其實我一直就會覺得，你說演技的比併是很難公平的。（連你胡杏兒都是這樣的？）對啊，胡杏兒是誰啊，胡杏兒不代表誰的。（惡評會寫甚麼？）甚麼回大陸撈金啊，那些都會寫。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/V9IgkyHveg4U7iMArSFaBQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS40NzM2ODQyMTA1MjY0/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-01/937ed930-4fde-11eb-bf7e-d0ff4ea4df7c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FV9IgkyHveg4U7iMArSFaBQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS40NzM2ODQyMTA1MjY0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-01%2F937ed930-4fde-11eb-bf7e-d0ff4ea4df7c&h=474ce417&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JH.SO4J3wnqmdMwKKf6z3A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEzNDQ-/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-01/aa9ecd00-4fde-11eb-beaf-f63a397a3409\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJH.SO4J3wnqmdMwKKf6z3A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEzNDQ-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-01%2Faa9ecd00-4fde-11eb-beaf-f63a397a3409&h=1c16ea5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港姐出身的杏兒在無綫年代一直很努力，試過極速變肥變瘦拍劇集《肥田囍事》，而她曾在2011年憑劇集《萬凰之王》及《怒火街頭》一連奪得三個獎項，成為「三料視后」。在2015年約滿離巢後，杏兒進軍內地，不過演出的劇集都是配角，暫時未擔正過主角。"},{"pid":"f6793a36e5b3461334e332d82d3ab291fb2b7bd9","tid":2356019,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"交齊稅未"},{"pid":"02f6ee0206d17045d4fafa44a31ec1845316e489","tid":2356019,"uid":292544,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:10:02.000Z","msg":"幾十歲塊閪鬆哂有機會都比廿歲果d"},{"pid":"dd6d08574c4bcdec03eb91d8f48c4b77f98b1251","tid":2356019,"uid":4811,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:22:25.000Z","msg":"有錢咪得囉，咪撚當自己戲劇家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87f5b9e6d0f6a347b8da299d6365fe9c0a1c5bf7","tid":2356019,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02f6ee0206d17045d4fafa44a31ec1845316e489","tid":2356019,"uid":292544,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:10:02.000Z","msg":"幾十歲塊閪鬆哂有機會都比廿歲果d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:27:47.000Z","msg":"同盧宛恩爭緊飯食仲想做女一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8493cbe7d072f2a34d7448cb38d836454a79691b","tid":2356019,"uid":229161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:30:50.000Z","msg":"下 上高唔係做三線配角都高片酬過香港做主角咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我見阿佘都無做主角喎"},{"pid":"5adeae72c155a270213f2a4948328